macro.name: DAQ_AI_PORT_NAME
macro.description: Port name for AI DAQ Port. Defaults to cDAQ9185-MUONFEMod3

macro.name: DAQ_AO_PORT_NAME
macro.description: Port name for AO DAQ Port. Defaults to cDAQ9185-MUONFEMod4

macro.name: FREQ
macro.description: Sample rate in Hz for reading separator voltage and current. Defaults to 1000

macro.name: NELM
macro.description: Number of samples read from separator voltage and current. Defaults to 100
